description: Welcome to 395 West 4th Street, an expansive 2,912-square-foot single-family home located in the heart of vibrant South Boston! Full of character and potential, this property presents a rare opportunity to restore and customize a beautiful home to suit your vision. The current layout features 5 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and a large partially finished basement, offering ample space and flexibility for future updates. Inside, you’ll find generous living areas with high ceilings and an abundance of natural light, ready to be transformed into your dream living space. Ideally situated just steps from South Boston’s finest amenities, trendy restaurants, cozy coffee shops, and boutique shopping, this home also provides convenient access to the Seaport District, downtown Boston, and major transit routes.  Don’t miss your chance to create a one-of-a-kind residence in this highly desirable neighborhood. The property is vacant and easy to show—please email to schedule a viewing today!
